children.name: We know the game because we’ve played it. From global brands to elite clubs and athletes, we’ve been on every side of the sponsorship table. That experience and our unrivalled network is what makes us different.
To provide the best experiences, The Chiliz Group

We cut out the fine-print traps and manage contracts so your spend is safe and every deal works in your favour, by negotiating contract terms, protecting against reputation risks, and ensuring deliverables fallback options are enforced.
When Access Matters, We’re Already Inside.

Sports sponsorship isn’t about luck. It’s about knowing who to call, what to say, and how to close. At Chiliz Sports, we’ve sat on your side of the table, so we know the risks, the shortcuts, and the people who actually move the needle.

Most agencies only promise it. We deliver. Our team has lived the challenges of sponsorship first-hand. We know how easy it is to waste months chasing introductions, hitting dead ends, or signing misaligned deals. That’s why we go straight to the decision-makers, define clear goals, and build activations that stick.

We’ve been the sponsor, the negotiator, and the client and along the way we’ve built the trust of 70+ of the biggest names in sport. Those relationships give us credibility where it counts: with clubs, leagues, talent, and the people making the calls. Others are still pitching to get in the room. We’re already there. Now, we put that advantage to work for you — helping brands navigate the sports maze and secure partnerships that deliver.

Go straight to the decision-makers from 70+ top clubs and leagues. We know who matters and we know how to get you in front of them. Whether it’s club owners, league executives, or  athletes, we make sure your brand connects directly with the people who can say yes.
